joyous /ˈdʒɔɪəs/

1. ADJ Joyous means extremely happy. 非常快乐的 [文学性] 

例： She had made their childhood so joyous and carefree. 她使他们的童年生活非常快乐、无忧无虑。 

2. joyously ADV 非常快乐地 

例： Sarah accepted joyously. 萨拉非常快乐地接受了。

